text: Abraham Morris (1752 – 13 February 1822) was an Irish banker. He sat in the Irish House of Commons for County Cork from 1791 to 1797.E. M. Johnston-Liik, History of the Irish Parliament 1692–1800, vol. title: Abraham Morris
